item.description:
@O_M_G1 wrote:

client.java:14038: ';' expected public void update() ^

For this, add a }above the update void

client.java:14041: 'else' without 'if' {else{ ^
Replace the {before else with }

client.java:13091: illegal start of expression public boolean pickUpItem(int item, int amount) ^
Add a }above the boolean

client.java:18624: orphaned case case 128: //Trade Request
Meh, add a break; or a } above it

client.java:20875: illegal start of expression private int somejunk; ^
Add a } above it

client.java:14038: ';' expected public void update() ^

client.java:14041: 'else' without 'if' {else{

I already told you how to fix the last two
